metadata.description:
1) data sets including short chain chlorinated paraffins, perfluorochemicals persistent organic pollutants (remobilised) in central qinghai-tibet plateau grassland typical food chain "grass - pika - raptor" occurrence and pollution characteristics of data;
2) short chain chlorinated paraffins by gas chromatography - mass spectrometry determination of perfluorinated compounds by liquid chromatography - mass spectrometry determination;
3) data set including the concentration of total organic carbon in the soil, the region each trophic level in the food chain, carbon and nitrogen stable isotope ratio and trophic level of precision is obtained by isotope data.
4) samples of the concentration of the raptor perfluorinated compounds in muscle and characteristic data is divided into two parts, chest muscles and the leg muscles, also including the raptor concentration data of feathers;
5) sample concentration of short chain chlorinated paraffins data in addition to each trophic level of muscle tissue, also including the raptor levels in the gastric volume data.
